raw.subject: MBIST tests embedded memories in ARM-based products. MBIST performs sequences of reads and writes to memory according to a test algorithm. This book is for engineers who want to use the MBIST controller to test the RAM blocks in Cortex-A9 processors. Some knowledge of the AXI protocol is required.
